{"tid":1391312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盾牌貼國旗國徽","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:50:50.000Z","uid":67295,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"afa8f602a0bcb1250f569a5a15466b751e87d824","tid":1391312,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"前幾日去咗倫敦集會，有位絲打無連登Account但係又想俾下計所以幫佢post<br />\n<br />\n大家有無諗過將個國徽拎出街做盾牌，或者整啲貼紙痴係盾牌度。目的就係俾傳媒影到佢打落黎。<br />\n<br />\n一黎啲狗打人既時候可能都會諗一諗再扑落去<br />\n二黎可以造成輿論，記者朋友影到布機會分化到香港警察同中共，最少都落佢地面。甚至可以傳出國際，俾國際睇香港既對手係共產黨<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可！"},{"pid":"a78d5ff16826fe6fb4e70ebb66640f280654c500","tid":1391312,"uid":67295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c4583ef3e5cdbe465fc589e663aaddd9200012a","tid":1391312,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e16b853b15de761178a9afe0f6c778fb9873935","tid":1391312,"uid":251691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"借位擴盾Po<br />\n[遊戲攻略]香城Online盾牌系統：淺談歷史上的盾牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389067</a>"},{"pid":"74a64baea93e90a1318310cc835c9867e998cf74","tid":1391312,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82505d6f3927f0cc388e414c3aba7a9623dc9adc","tid":1391312,"uid":59753,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"咪on9"},{"pid":"71c94968aeae1d1da4a46be3da7f50a3bb8593d9","tid":1391312,"uid":67295,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"82505d6f3927f0cc388e414c3aba7a9623dc9adc","tid":1391312,"uid":59753,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"咪on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"真係唔work咩，我諗住可以造成輿論<img src=\"/assets/f